caption.p:
Effect of acetogenin-rich fraction of Annona muricata leaves (AFAL) on glutathione peroxidase (GPx) activity and reduced glutathione (GSH) concentration in testosterone propionate (TP)-induced BPH in rats. Values are expressed as mean ± standard error of mean ( n = 5).
# Significant when compared to normal control ( p < 0.05); *significant compared to TP control ( p < 0.05).
